Localization.Name: Sootho Gloves Vineland
Localization.Description: Pros at keeping your hands safe without sacrificing dexterity, the slip-resistant Sootho gloves deliver solid protection and lasting warmth during chilly or hostile conditions. The tough synthetic leather breaks in well and will stand up to years of frequent use.
